  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/c890f2588d9b58a8459054f1ab4be015.poster.avif?t=1769920627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/c890f2588d9b58a8459054f1ab4be015.webm?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/c890f2588d9b58a8459054f1ab4be015.mp4?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Onsui </strong>is a  cross between physics action games and strategic puzzlers. Drop, Match and Combine imps to grow them into a larger shape and increase your score. The more space you use, the harder it gets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It's got to be someone's job to sort out these mischevious imps, and it's up to you.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PHYSICS PUZZLER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/95ce312b25826507675bcd66f41692a1.poster.avif?t=1769920627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/95ce312b25826507675bcd66f41692a1.webm?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/95ce312b25826507675bcd66f41692a1.mp4?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold useful items in your offhand for later use!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REACH GREATER HIGHS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rack up points and achieve combos of combinations to reach new high scores.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/7192b084099c004ad9fca5ab7bf72a35.poster.avif?t=1769920627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/7192b084099c004ad9fca5ab7bf72a35.webm?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/7192b084099c004ad9fca5ab7bf72a35.mp4?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scoreboard to track recent and high scores</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Game Modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customisable Physics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique, consistent daily puzzle</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RISING OVERFLOW MODE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/bcc85bf66152e33e38d17e314cf02474.poster.avif?t=1769920627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/bcc85bf66152e33e38d17e314cf02474.webm?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/bcc85bf66152e33e38d17e314cf02474.mp4?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A faster-paced gamemode where the floor of the box is constantly rising! Merge Imps and quickly lower the floor to survive. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>IMPLOCK MODE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/33e56e511c8467c48c00d5be0cbd7254.poster.avif?t=1769920627\" width=600 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/33e56e511c8467c48c00d5be0cbd7254.webm?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/33e56e511c8467c48c00d5be0cbd7254.mp4?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A strategy-focused gamemode where you must merge your Imps up the rank with just Rank 2 Imps. When you're only able to drop one kind of Imp, how will you solve the puzzle and reach Rank 11, or a new high score?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Daily Puzzles</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every day, a unique puzzle is available. This puzzle can be replayed over and over for the entirety of the day, and the order of objects you merge will be the same each time. This puzzle resets as soon as the date changes, for a unique puzzle each and every day.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/c890f2588d9b58a8459054f1ab4be015.poster.avif?t=1769920627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/c890f2588d9b58a8459054f1ab4be015.webm?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/c890f2588d9b58a8459054f1ab4be015.mp4?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Onsui </strong>is a  cross between physics action games and strategic puzzlers. Drop, Match and Combine imps to grow them into a larger shape and increase your score. The more space you use, the harder it gets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>It's got to be someone's job to sort out these mischevious imps, and it's up to you.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PHYSICS PUZZLER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/95ce312b25826507675bcd66f41692a1.poster.avif?t=1769920627\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/95ce312b25826507675bcd66f41692a1.webm?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/95ce312b25826507675bcd66f41692a1.mp4?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hold useful items in your offhand for later use!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REACH GREATER HIGHS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rack up points and achieve combos of combinations to reach new high scores.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span c