ss=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/33e56e511c8467c48c00d5be0cbd7254.poster.avif?t=1769920627\" width=600 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/33e56e511c8467c48c00d5be0cbd7254.webm?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704910/extras/33e56e511c8467c48c00d5be0cbd7254.mp4?t=1769920627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A strategy-focused gamemode where you must merge your Imps up the rank with just Rank 2 Imps. When you're only able to drop one kind of Imp, how will you solve the puzzle and reach Rank 11, or a new high score?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>Daily Puzzles</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every day, a unique puzzle is available. This puzzle can be replayed over and over for the entirety of the day, and the order of objects you merge will be the same each time. This puzzle resets as soon as the date changes, for a unique puzzle each and every day.</p>",
